title: 820-00281 no power
message:
You must provide more relevant information.
3V3_SUS requires PM_SLP_SUS_L presence and that signal doesn't appear directly.
Post 3V3_G3H, R7020 and F7000 voltages.
Any USB-C port has different symptom than others?
Use USB-C V/I meter to compare.
